title: Beat Doom Bots and still no icon
body: hey so i beat doom bots but havent received my little devil teemo icon im jw if there is a delay on it being sent out or if it its a glitch?{{item:3070}}

replies.body: and I did not get the icon devil teemo.

The [Official Teemoing 2016 Announcement](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016) mentions that these are being delivered until November 17th. If you don't have anything *after* the 17th rolls by, please let me know.
